column5: Heading up there tomorrow, anyone else goin?
Wish I could.  Never been there.  I know there is a lot of stuff I need   as well.  Although I did do a bit of damage at Lebaron on Sunday.
When does the big sale start?  I thought it was sometime in March?

I am waiting till the spring spectacular starts after the 29th.... I will probably go after March 6th to trade in a couple of reels.  If you haven't been though plan on spending more than a couple of hours LOL.
The Main Guys from the NextBIte are going to be there on Mar2nd.  F Y I  David  aka  Superdad
